<p><a href="#sdfootnote27anc" name="sdfootnote27sym">27</a>These topics can be found in the writings of Sigmund Freud, in the context of the relation between the anal zone and the superego, and in Jacques Lacan’s analyses of the forms of the <em>objet petit a</em>. See Lacan, <em>Anxiety: The Seminar of Jacques Lacan</em>, <em>Book X</em>, ed. Jacques-Alain Miller, trans. A. R. Price (Cambridge, MA: Polity Press, 2015), 294–309.</p>
